## HOW TO RESUME THIS SESSION
================================================================================

Claude Code saves conversation history automatically as JSONL under:
  ~/.claude/projects/-home-cicero-proj-Zoolandia/<uuid>.jsonl

To resume: run  claude --resume  in the project directory.
Claude Code will list recent sessions; select this one.

Alternatively, the persistent memory at:
  ~/.claude/projects/-home-cicero-proj-Zoolandia/memory/MEMORY.md
is loaded automatically at the start of every new session.

